&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Advert Details – Band 7 Acute Pain Nurse Specialist &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking to appoint to the position of Lead Acute Pain Nurse Specialist to join our established Acute Pain team which consists of consultant anaesthetists and nurse specialists with a special interest in pain management. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for an experienced Registered Nurse with an interest in pain management. The specialities that you will be working within include Cardiac surgery, Thoracic surgery and Upper Gastrointestinal surgery. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The specialities that you will be working within include Cardiac surgery, Thoracic surgery and Upper Gastrointestinal surgery. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is an excellent opportunity to work at Liverpool Heart and Chest Hospital NHS Foundation Trust. We are a specialist Cardiac, Cardiology and Cardiothoracic Trust which has received consistent “outstanding” ratings by the CQC.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Trust is committed to your personal and professional development with many opportunities on offer. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for candidates who share our passion for patient and family centered care, have a strong belief in influencing the quality agenda, whilst supporting the development of nursing and medical colleagues alike. If you want to make a difference and be part of an outstanding team we look forward to your application.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Part time and flexible working requests will be considered.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you want to make a difference and be part of an outstanding team, please apply&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
